    <owl:Class rdf:about="https://example.org/roadsigns#RoadSign">
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">The central taxonomic hierarchy organized according to the functional and legal roles defined in the Vienna Convention.

A sign placed beside or above roads to give instructions or provide information to road users, conformant with Part I, Annex 1 of the Vienna Convention on Road Signs and Signals (2006).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Road Sign</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


